He continued to run and fire, on Unicron.

::DrillBit::

He continued to fire on Unitron.

::Dollon::

He also continued to fire on Unitron, while scraming about his now
missing arm.

::Epyon::

He kept studying the holo map. The city would be perfect.

::Demolition::

He found Havoc. 
"He commander, whats up?"

::KitKat2::

She made her way to the main exit of the Alliance base. Hopefully she
could get out when someone used it.
